      <odd id="aspace_18dce3334ee4e10e8bcebe445a5b9839">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 38-B (YRG 38-B), Records documenting specific sports at Yale.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_540f73308a7601f8c54e04bd1f1d3b06">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were gifts of various donors, 1979-1986; transferred from the Department of Athletics, 2005; and transferred from the University of New Hampshire Library, 2018.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_ed0f9e03b532f315ea31cdd07c97ca76">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is partially restricted. See Collection Contents for details. Scrapbooks, Accession 2006-A-111, are available on microfilm. Patrons must use HM 180 instead of the originals.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_ef472a8a126ec45eaa79711d8c6e07dc">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Department of Athletics, Yale University, Records Documenting Baseball (RU 61). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_d2be356eebabcffcb281e000c2b6be53">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_1c8af81318d6cbc85ad1e54814c1dde8">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of reports, score books, publications, and scrapbooks maintained primarily by the Department of Athletics documenting baseball at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <altformavail id="aspace_1f724e55c7dc4dc3476263e1ee15a293">
         <head>Existence and Location of Copies</head>
         <p>Scrapbooks, Accession 2006-A-111, are available on microfilm.</p>  
      </altformavail>
